Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有時間畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.76,0:19:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很舒坦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是嘛 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我們打到賽點了 Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我就打到這了 英雄
