Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,全身的細胞都在狂喜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,它們在命令我讓我加速
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,加速 加速
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,英雄好像是理所當然般地急速成長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,接著又漸漸離我而去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,無須畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,根本無須畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,特別好
